{"id":50366,"title":"[Diabetes and tobacco, a dangerous combination].","abstract":"Smoking is a worldwide health problem. In regular smokers, the risk of developing type 2 diabetes is high. In people with diabetes, smoking significantly worsens microangiopathic, cardio- and cerebrovascular complications.Therefore, helping people with diabetes or at risk of diabetes to give up smoking is crucial.","date":"2014-05-06","categories":"Endocrine System Diseases","split":"train","url":"http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/24796074","annotations":[{"name":"Diabetes mellitus type 2","weight":0.812688,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Diabetes_mellitus_type_2"},{"name":"Diabetes mellitus","weight":0.797552,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Diabetes_mellitus"},{"name":"Smoking","weight":0.759859,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Smoking"},{"name":"Cerebrovascular disease","weight":0.626563,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Cerebrovascular_disease"},{"name":"Tobacco smoking","weight":0.604378,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Tobacco_smoking"},{"name":"Health","weight":0.5771,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Health"},{"name":"Tobacco","weight":0.545124,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Tobacco"},{"name":"Risk","weight":0.312673,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Risk"},{"name":"Complication (medicine)","weight":0.190315,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Complication_(medicine)"},{"name":"Microangiopathy","weight":0.0163827,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Microangiopathy"},{"name":"Aerobic exercise","weight":0.015901,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Aerobic_exercise"}]}
